{"tid":1307682,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"合和實業主席:東大嶼是寶藏","createTime":"2019-07-11T16:19:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T18:03:30.000Z","uid":215417,"like":0,"dislike":60,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"aa5a914b9e0789f88261dbed105c0ad8f486cf22","tid":1307682,"uid":215417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T16:19:32.000Z","msg":"合和實業私有化後，主席胡應湘首次接受專訪談到香港大勢。他認為財富嚴重傾斜至政府及發展商，是種種社會問題的主因。他打開地圖一指，強調填海是改變香港命運的重中之重，形容東大嶼是寶藏，附近一帶水淺，而且位置鄰近中環和尖沙咀：「香港要生存，一定要連結大灣區。年輕一輩不會想，填海不是為了我們發展商。我都83歲了，填海工程結束時可能已經蒙主寵召。我是香港第三代，提議填海是為了香港人。」<br />\n <br />\n作為政府推行明日大嶼背後一位重要推動者，合和主席胡應湘形容東大嶼是「寶藏」；<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">至於白海豚生存危機，他笑說：「如果你放泥落海，白海豚唔識走，嗰條係蠢嘅白海豚，唔見咗你都唔會可惜。」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mCmWE81.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmCmWE81.png&h=5026e65d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSource:蘋果facebook<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都唔知你條老野係到up乜春"},{"pid":"6a9e74e2a9fbe8b3d614e5f628e8ac0636781dd3","tid":1307682,"uid":215417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T16:19:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3832166beec4f9617d1f53566ce2aef5ecb339e3","tid":1307682,"uid":215417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T16:20:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b688a82717499ad78c804d98d79eb75ff8c8cc76","tid":1307682,"uid":215417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T16:21:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"939ecd1a6e17325bdcf0a082eed7be299d958975","tid":1307682,"uid":215417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T16:21:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"eb0d61e723cc04a792626cd17511b56602a8ae84","tid":1307682,"uid":215417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T16:23:36.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"624890434ccdebcb24d5b60fb2fb7b672d7ff038","tid":1307682,"uid":215417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":